com.example.buber.Model

Class UserLocation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.buber.Model.UserLocation

  • public class UserLocation
extends java.lang.Object
    Used to represent a location that can be parsed by Google's map API. Currently just a latitude and longitude with some simple methods for calculating distance between locations.
